MODULE: src/utils
FILES: file-utils.js, heartbeat-manager.js, logger.js, markdown-v2-formatter.js, ansi-adapter.js, output-segmenter.js
RESPONSIBILITY: Utility functions — logging, file ops, Telegram formatting, ANSI processing, smart segmentation
INTERFACES:
- logger: createLogger(module) -> Logger
- file-utils: readJson, writeJson, mkdirp
- markdown-v2-formatter: escapeMarkdownV2(text), convertToMarkdownV2(text)
- ansi-adapter: stripAnsi(text), collapseCarriageReturns(text), processChunk(text) -> F-020
- output-segmenter: segmentOutput(text, maxChunkSize?) -> string[] -> F-020
DEPENDENCIES:
- uses: pino: Logging
SUBDIRS:
- src/utils/ansi-adapter.prizm -> L2 detail for ANSI adapter
- src/utils/output-segmenter.prizm -> L2 detail for output segmenter
UPDATED: 2026-03-22
